tip.text: One of the few places in Singapore with the black sheep ale. Yummy food, nice ambience! Parking at Cluny Court a tad expensive though.
A variety of traditional costumes to suit all ages! Prices are very reasonable and services very professional! We had fun doing our family shoot here!
A simple one-dish menu consisting of noodles in a pork bone broth with generous servings of pork for just 7000Won! Non-spicy soup version available for kids/non-spicy eaters..
Beer's great! 6 beers on tap. Get your prepaid card and pull how much you want! Damn awesome!
